1.6 Species value

The FDI catch table was analyzed to return the estimates of the average price per species and year, that is further compared with the average price calculated per country (by species). Furthermore, in order to compare total weight landings and total value landings, the cases with total landings > 0 but landings value = 0 were identified and reported in a table, were available.
